Body: Description: Hello, I have issued a dozen or so uninstall commands/actions through the server and none of them seem to be working. I can see that the action was sent but it does not look like it ultimately goes through.

What We've Learned Updated: 12.05
The EPP Client is not communicating with the EPP Server. We asked the customer to check the license availability and the network connections.

Next Steps Updated: 12.05
Waiting for the customer to answer.

14.05
